g":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"debf0fbe0da2d74360afd4f1444691784bf3297a","tid":1827301,"uid":3976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"341dd6ccff49408b191ee3917b38c24983943147","tid":1827301,"uid":29093,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T00:44:47.000Z","msg":"北角狗屋喺隔離， 小心癲狗亂咬人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T02:20:32.000Z","msg":"請張華峰個女食tg<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdc4aae5faeef344080a2fb8e986d62bc08311ad","tid":1827301,"uid":264077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T02:40:01.000Z","msg":"開支開檳去悼念先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57f7142137a3fa474586e44a4a2a609e4f7d37a7","tid":1827301,"uid":25951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T02:46:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/amp/news/realtime/hk/1669557\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Famp%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1669557&d=yrakYkBpMe8E3VCHF0kcyl8MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=0cec3694\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Famp%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1669557&h=553a5307\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/amp/news/realtime/hk/1669557</a><br />\n<br />\n立法會金融服務界議員張華峰的22歲孻女，上周四從半山寓所高處墮下身亡。張華峰昨通知一眾親朋好友，指愛女的喪禮將於位於北角的香港殯儀館舉行，下月17日設靈，18日上午舉行大殮儀式。<br />\n<br />\n張華峰在訊息上提到，自知年近歲晚，大家會很忙，倘若親友未能撥冗出席喪禮，亦可奉送花圈致哀，相信愛女會感受到大家的關愛，知道除了家人外，仍有很多朋友和世叔伯都十分疼愛她，讓愛女開開心心上路。<br />\n<br />\n張華峰育有三名女兒，不幸離世的孻女患上躁鬱症已有兩年，事發後張華峰曾形容孻女「好乖，好孝順」，並指她原本在英國讀書，患上躁鬱症便回港醫病，看過不少醫生，病情「時好時壞」。對於女兒離世，他當時亦坦言「唔知點解會咁」。"},{"pid":"41bde7b6cad7d5755eae42a28992cfcf13540790","tid":1827301,"uid":66202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3aa46412fa1d2a16fab5403653beb77c1779cb83","tid":1827301,"uid":283541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"892d89d7e059f57637063c257bbe58db32382446","tid":1827301,"uid":66202,"like":0